data.description: Don't miss out on this one. Great home in a quiet neighborhood. This one is almost completely renovated. There's still a few things that could be done but not many. The roof is just over 7 years old, the central heat & air was replaced this past summer and the water heater was replaced this month. New waterproof vinyl plank flooring in the kitchen, laundry room, living room and hallway. Ceramic tile in the doorway and hall bathroom. Hurry before this one is gone!
